Package org.blockchainnative.metadata

Class EventFieldInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.blockchainnative.metadata.EventFieldInfo
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    EthereumEventFieldInfo, FabricEventFieldInfo
    public class EventFieldInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds additional information about a field of a class which is used as smart contract event type.

    It is recommended to use ContractInfoBuilder and its subtypes to construct instances of this class.
    Since:
    1.0
    See Also:
    ContractInfoBuilder, ContractInfo, ContractWrapperGenerator
